Holotype: female, K 884, vicinity of Jayapura, under the leaf sheath of undetermined grass (
Poaceae
), 1.XI. 2011, specimen in a black circle. Paratypes: 1 female on the same slide; 3 females on other slides and series of unmounted females and larvae in acet-ethanol; all with the same collecting data as holotype.
